member.returns:
The Folder Access Control List of domains for the Account, e.g.

{
"AccessControlType" : "AllowedDomains",
"Domains": ["domainA", "domainB"]
}

The Folder Access Control List of domains for the Account, e.g.

{
"AccessControlType" : "AllowedDomains",
"Domains": ["domainA", "domainB"]
}

